Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.98,0:00:20.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,So I am back in Australia,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.98,0:00:20.64,CHN,,0,0,0,,我又回到了澳大利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.64,0:00:21.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,and, of course, I'm a reminded
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.74,0:00:24.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,that everything in this country is trying to kill you,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.64,0:00:24.17,CHN,,0,0,0,,我牢记着这个国家有太多致命的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.17,0:00:26.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,particularly snakes and spiders,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.17,0:00:26.02,CHN,,0,0,0,,特别是蛇和蜘蛛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.02,0:00:28.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,and here at the Australian Reptile Park
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.02,0:00:28.23,CHN,,0,0,0,,而在澳大利亚爬行动物公园这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.23,0:00:30.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,they actually milk snakes and spiders
