Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.13,0:02:49.46,CHN,,0,0,0,,-我的手开始抽筋了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.46,0:02:50.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna put him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.46,0:02:50.29,CHN,,0,0,0,,得把它关回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.29,0:02:52.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,So I'll get you guys to jump back for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.29,0:02:52.17,CHN,,0,0,0,,你可以退两步腾点地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.17,0:02:53.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,And this is the sketchy bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.17,0:02:53.53,CHN,,0,0,0,,下一步就很简单了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.53,0:02:54.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.53,0:02:54.36,CHN,,0,0,0,,-恩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:55.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,When you get him out, you got the hook,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:55.60,CHN,,0,0,0,,弄它出来时能用钩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.60,0:02:57.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,when you're putting him back,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.60,0:02:57.53,CHN,,0,0,0,,可是把它放回去的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:02:58.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,it's just who's quicker.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:02:58.73,CHN,,0,0,0,,就是看谁更快了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:01.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:01.27,CHN,,0,0,0,,预备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.43,0:03:05.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.43,0:03:05.51,CHN,,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.82,0:03:08.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,Are your hands trembling a little bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.82,0:03:08.76,CHN,,0,0,0,,- 手发抖了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.76,0:03:11.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.76,0:03:11.95,CHN,,0,0,0,,- 嗯，每次都是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.95,0:03:13.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,So how much venom do you actually need
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.68,0:03:15.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,to make antivenom?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.95,0:03:15.18,CHN,,0,0,0,,那制作抗毒血清究竟需要多少毒液呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:16.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,About 15.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:16.38,CHN,,0,0,0,,-大概15条蛇的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:18.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,15 snakes to make one vial of antivenom?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:18.50,CHN,,0,0,0,,一小瓶抗毒血清用15条蛇的毒液制造？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.50,0:03:20.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.50,0:03:20.09,CHN,,0,0,0,,-是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:22.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,Venom evolved from saliva
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:22.05,CHN,,0,0,0,,毒液是由唾液进化而来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:25.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,and it's used primarily for catching and digesting prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:25.69,CHN,,0,0,0,,主要用来捕捉和消化猎物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.69,0:03:28.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,Each species of snake has a different venom
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.69,0:03:28.37,CHN,,0,0,0,,每种蛇的毒液都不同
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.37,0:03:31.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,tailored to the specific animals they hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.37,0:03:31.78,CHN,,0,0,0,,都是为它们的猎物量身定制的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.78,0:03:33.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,The venom was originally squirted
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.78,0:03:33.75,CHN,,0,0,0,,最初的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:36.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,into a snake's mouth by the back teeth,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:36.37,CHN,,0,0,0,,毒液由蛇的后牙喷入蛇口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.37,0:03:37.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,and to this day,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.37,0:03:37.31,CHN,,0,0,0,,如今
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.31,0:03:40.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,almost 2/3 of all snakes are rear fanged.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.31,0:03:40.80,CHN,,0,0,0,,差不多2/3的蛇  毒牙都在后方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:42.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now why the rear tooth, you might ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:42.96,CHN,,0,0,0,,所以你可能会问  为啥是后牙嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.96,0:03:45.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, it's because the venom gland itself
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.43,0:03:47.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,is actually behind the snake's eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.96,0:03:47.72,CHN,,0,0,0,,因为蛇的毒腺实际上长在眼睛后面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.72,0:03:50.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,So the shortest distance for a duct
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.72,0:03:50.32,CHN,,0,0,0,,所以对于毒液导管来说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.32,0:03:55.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,is directly downwards to the back end of the top jaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.32,0:03:55.12,CHN,,0,0,0,,最短距离就是直接向下延伸到上颚的后端
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.12,0:03:56.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,In some species,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.12,0:03:56.30,CHN,,0,0,0,,对于某些品种
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:59.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,evolutionary pressures caused the fangs to move closer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:59.23,CHN,,0,0,0,,进化的压力迫使毒牙前移
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:01.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,and closer to the front of the jaw,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:01.28,CHN,,0,0,0,,逐渐靠近上颚的前端
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:05.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,improving the snake's ability to catch and kill prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:05.04,CHN,,0,0,0,,这提高了蛇捕捉和击杀猎物的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.04,0:04:07.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,While the location of the fangs was evolving,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.04,0:04:07.60,CHN,,0,0,0,,在毒牙位置发生改变的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:09.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,so were the fangs themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:09.67,CHN,,0,0,0,,毒牙本身也在进化
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.67,0:04:12.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,They started off as smooth ordinary teeth
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.67,0:04:12.32,CHN,,0,0,0,,毒牙最初只是光滑的普通牙齿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.32,0:04:15.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,with venom flowing down the outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.32,0:04:15.03,CHN,,0,0,0,,毒液顺着毒牙的表面流下来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.03,0:04:16.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,but over time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.03,0:04:16.20,CHN,,0,0,0,,但时过境迁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.20,0:04:19.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,some snake lineages evolved a groove in each fang
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.20,0:04:19.55,CHN,,0,0,0,,有些蛇的毒牙  进化出了一个凹槽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.56,0:04:21.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,to channel the flow of venom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.56,0:04:21.70,CHN,,0,0,0,,用来为毒液导流
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.70,0:04:24.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,In some species, the groove became deeper and deeper
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.70,0:04:24.94,CHN,,0,0,0,,某些物种的蛇  凹槽变得越来越深
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.94,0:04:28.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,eventually closing in to form a hollow tube,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.94,0:04:28.13,CHN,,0,0,0,,最终闭合成了中空的导管
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.13,0:04:32.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,and now the teeth literally inject venom into prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.13,0:04:32.37,CHN,,0,0,0,,所以实际上  毒牙是将毒液“注射”到猎物的体内
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:33.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,But this is not the norm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:33.92,CHN,,0,0,0,,这并不是普遍现象
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.92,0:04:37.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,Only 1/7 of the world's snakes have hollow fangs,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.92,0:04:37.65,CHN,,0,0,0,,全球范围内只有1/7的蛇拥有中空的毒牙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:40.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,but, of course, almost all the venomous snakes in Australia
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:40.66,CHN,,0,0,0,,当然 澳洲的几乎所有毒蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.66,0:04:42.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,do have hollow fangs,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.66,0:04:42.34,CHN,,0,0,0,,都有这种高级毒牙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:45.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,so we set up this macro shot to take a closer look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:45.42,CHN,,0,0,0,,所以我们安排了微距镜头  给它来个近距离特写
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.42,0:04:46.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,This one's rolling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.42,0:04:46.72,CHN,,0,0,0,,这边好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:47.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,That one's rolling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:47.68,CHN,,0,0,0,,那边也好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:48.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,We're ready when you're.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:48.65,CHN,,0,0,0,,你们好了我们就开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.65,0:04:49.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,We're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.65,0:04:49.72,CHN,,0,0,0,,我们好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:50.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:50.55,CHN,,0,0,0,,完美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:54.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right, everyone's ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:54.47,CHN,,0,0,0,,那么  都准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:00.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:00.92,CHN,,0,0,0,,哇哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.92,0:05:03.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's got like jets
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.92,0:05:03.08,CHN,,0,0,0,,就像个喷嘴一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.08,0:05:04.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jets of venom coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.08,0:05:04.98,CHN,,0,0,0,,这喷涌而出的毒液啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.98,0:05:06.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Has this guy not been milked in a while or?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.98,0:05:06.70,CHN,,0,0,0,,这家伙多久没挤毒液了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:08.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's been a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:08.31,CHN,,0,0,0,,是啊  有点久了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:14.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,Not only do we have some of the most toxic snakes on the planet here,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:14.94,CHN,,0,0,0,,我们这儿不仅有全地表毒性最强的蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.94,0:05:16.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,we also selectively breed them
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.94,0:05:16.35,CHN,,0,0,0,,为了制造抗蛇毒血清
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:18.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,for the production of antivenom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:18.47,CHN,,0,0,0,,还对它们进行了选择性育种
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.47,0:05:19.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,They're bred to produce more venom
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:20.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,than their wild counterparts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.47,0:05:20.98,CHN,,0,0,0,,使得它们能产生的毒液比野生同类更多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:23.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,So some of our coastal taipans are producing five, six
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:23.88,CHN,,0,0,0,,所以我们这儿培育的太攀蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:26.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,nearly seven times what their wild counterpart would,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:26.38,CHN,,0,0,0,,毒液产量是野生同类的五  六  甚至七倍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.38,0:05:27.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,and that's just from selective breeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.38,0:05:27.65,CHN,,0,0,0,,这正是选择性育种的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.65,0:05:29.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,You find your two most psychotic ones,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.65,0:05:29.02,CHN,,0,0,0,,选出两个最疯的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.02,0:05:29.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,you put them together,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.02,0:05:29.85,CHN,,0,0,0,,让它俩繁殖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:31.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,you hope for the best and the absolute worst comes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:31.85,CHN,,0,0,0,,你抱着最好的期望  然而绝对会出现最坏的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:34.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,So keeps you on your toes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:34.43,CHN,,0,0,0,,所以  别高兴得太早
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:35.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,That sounds horrendous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:35.45,CHN,,0,0,0,,听起来好嚇人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.45,0:05:36.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,So you're saying that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.45,0:05:36.61,CHN,,0,0,0,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.61,0:05:38.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,these are the most venomous snakes in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.61,0:05:38.84,CHN,,0,0,0,,这儿本就有地球上最毒的蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.84,0:05:41.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,and then you have bred them to be more venomous?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.84,0:05:41.88,CHN,,0,0,0,,你还把它们培育得更毒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:43.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they're super snakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:43.98,CHN,,0,0,0,,没错  它们是超级毒蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.89,0:05:47.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,A scratch from any of these animals could kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.89,0:05:47.12,CHN,,0,0,0,,被这些动物随便划一下就会寄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:49.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,And some of these snakes are giving 4.5,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:49.63,CHN,,0,0,0,,这里有的蛇 一口能喷 4.5
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.63,0:05:51.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,4.9 grams of venom per bite,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.63,0:05:51.63,CHN,,0,0,0,,4.9 克的毒液
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:53.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,which is just stupid amounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:53.66,CHN,,0,0,0,,量大得惊人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:55.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,We spoke to venom expert, Timothy Jackson
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:55.91,CHN,,0,0,0,,我们与毒液专家  蒂莫西·杰克森进行了谈话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:58.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,who argued these snakes produce more venom
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:58.30,CHN,,0,0,0,,他提出质疑说 这些蛇能生产更多的毒液
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:06:01.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,because they are regularly milked, unlike wild snakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:06:01.91,CHN,,0,0,0,,是因为它们经常被挤毒液  而野生蛇不会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.91,0:06:05.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,Either way, the snakes in this room contain more venom
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.91,0:06:05.37,CHN,,0,0,0,,无论如何  这房间里的蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.37,0:06:08.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,than virtually any others on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.37,0:06:08.15,CHN,,0,0,0,,几乎拥有全地表最高的毒液产能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.15,0:06:10.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,We house the second, the third, the fourth, the fifth,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.15,0:06:10.75,CHN,,0,0,0,,我们这儿有毒蛇排行榜中第二到第五
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:12.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,and about the 12th or 13th most toxic,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:12.44,CHN,,0,0,0,,和大概第十二或者第十三的蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.44,0:06:14.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,depending on who you talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.44,0:06:14.69,CHN,,0,0,0,,得看你跟谁比了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.69,0:06:16.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,One bite from a King Cobra
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.69,0:06:16.41,CHN,,0,0,0,,眼镜王蛇的一口毒液
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:19.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,contains enough venom to kill 13,000 mice,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:19.94,CHN,,0,0,0,,足以杀死13000只老鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:23.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,and we know this because of a study from 1979
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:23.04,CHN,,0,0,0,,这得从1979年的一个研究说起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:26.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,that tested the venoms of 25 different species of snake
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:26.18,CHN,,0,0,0,,研究者取了25条不同种类蛇的毒液
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.18,0:06:27.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,on lab mice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.18,0:06:27.79,CHN,,0,0,0,,在小白鼠身上测量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.79,0:06:29.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,From this, we can estimate
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.79,0:06:29.17,CHN,,0,0,0,,实验结果表明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.17,0:06:31.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,that the venom from one King Cobra bite
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.17,0:06:31.09,CHN,,0,0,0,,眼镜王蛇的一口毒液
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.09,0:06:33.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,could kill around four humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.09,0:06:33.70,CHN,,0,0,0,,差不多可以杀死四个人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:34.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,though to be precise,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:34.98,CHN,,0,0,0,,虽然准确来说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.98,0:06:37.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,we'd have to say four human-sized rodents
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.98,0:06:37.83,CHN,,0,0,0,,是四个与人类同体积的啮齿动物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:41.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,because thankfully, no one's tested these venoms on humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:41.65,CHN,,0,0,0,,因为谢天谢地  没人真的在人身上做实验
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.65,0:06:42.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,And by this measure,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.65,0:06:42.93,CHN,,0,0,0,,按照这样的算法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.93,0:06:46.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,the most venomous snake in the world is the inland taipan,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.93,0:06:46.75,CHN,,0,0,0,,世界上最毒的蛇是内陆太攀蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.75,0:06:50.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,which conveniently lives in the middle of Australia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.75,0:06:50.62,CHN,,0,0,0,,它们生活在澳洲中部附近
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.62,0:06:52.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,A bite from the inland taipan
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.62,0:06:52.16,CHN,,0,0,0,,内陆太攀蛇的一口毒液
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.16,0:06:55.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,has enough venom to kill half a million mice,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.16,0:06:55.52,CHN,,0,0,0,,足以杀死五十万只老鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.52,0:06:57.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,or more than 100 humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.52,0:06:57.91,CHN,,0,0,0,,或者说  一百多个人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.91,0:07:01.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,So yeah, why not milk that one next?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.91,0:07:01.33,CHN,,0,0,0,,那么  下一条不妨就是它了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:03.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,So the next one, we're gonna step it up another notch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:03.34,CHN,,0,0,0,,接下来这条 我们要上点档次了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:05.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,So this is the inland taipan,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:05.13,CHN,,0,0,0,,这条就是内陆太攀蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:06.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,also known as the fierce snake,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:06.51,CHN,,0,0,0,,也被称为凶猛蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.51,0:07:08.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,the most toxic land snake on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.51,0:07:08.89,CHN,,0,0,0,,是地球上毒性最强的陆生蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.89,0:07:11.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,These guys have the ability with one drop of venom
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.89,0:07:11.32,CHN,,0,0,0,,这些家伙只要一滴毒液
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.32,0:07:13.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,to knock over 100 adult humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.32,0:07:13.35,CHN,,0,0,0,,就足以干掉 100 多位成年人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.35,0:07:15.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,So stupidly toxic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.35,0:07:15.49,CHN,,0,0,0,,超级超级剧毒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:16.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,So quite a lot smaller
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:18.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,than the last couple of animals we've used,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:18.24,CHN,,0,0,0,,它比我们刚才那几条小不少
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.24,0:07:20.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,but makes up for it in toxicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.24,0:07:20.13,CHN,,0,0,0,,但毒性弥补了这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.13,0:07:23.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,Very, very quick and very naughty when he wants to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.13,0:07:23.09,CHN,,0,0,0,,这家伙性情顽劣 动作迅猛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.09,0:07:24.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,but an absolutely gorgeous pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.09,0:07:24.84,CHN,,0,0,0,,但也相当优雅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.08,0:07:27.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,You can grab that bit for me, mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.08,0:07:27.18,CHN,,0,0,0,,伙计 帮我抓住那里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.18,0:07:28.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.18,0:07:28.01,CHN,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:29.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna grab this vial from behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:29.79,CHN,,0,0,0,,我得拿上你身后这个小杯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.69,0:07:31.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,And as you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.69,0:07:31.52,CHN,,0,0,0,,如你所见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.52,0:07:32.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,he's very keen on the killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.52,0:07:32.82,CHN,,0,0,0,,它相当热衷于杀戮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.09,0:07:36.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.09,0:07:36.92,CHN,,0,0,0,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.92,0:07:38.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,That is extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.92,0:07:38.77,CHN,,0,0,0,,这真是非同寻常
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:41.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,The most venomous snake in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:41.28,CHN,,0,0,0,,世界上最毒的蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:46.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,Just incredible animals, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:46.31,CHN,,0,0,0,,真是令人难以致信的生物 是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:48.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,(cage door shuts)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:48.92,CHN,,0,0,0,,（关上笼门）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.92,0:07:49.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,(laughs)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.92,0:07:49.94,CHN,,0,0,0,,（笑声）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.94,0:07:50.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,That was quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.94,0:07:50.78,CHN,,0,0,0,,很快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:52.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, those ones make me proper nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:52.13,CHN,,0,0,0,,是啊 这真让我紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.13,0:07:52.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't know about you guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.13,0:07:52.96,CHN,,0,0,0,,我不知道你们什么感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:53.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,but I'm sweating.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:53.79,CHN,,0,0,0,,但是我都冒冷汗了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.79,0:07:55.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,Can you see the hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.79,0:07:55.40,CHN,,0,0,0,,你知道你的手在抖吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:57.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,The moment I stop doing that after a milking
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:57.39,CHN,,0,0,0,,如果哪天  我挤完后手不抖了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:07:59.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,is the day I quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:07:59.11,CHN,,0,0,0,,八成是我见阎王了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.24,0:08:03.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,The concept of the most venomous snake is complicated
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.24,0:08:03.52,CHN,,0,0,0,,「最毒的蛇」的概念其实很复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.52,0:08:06.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,because snakes evolved their venom specifically
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.52,0:08:06.12,CHN,,0,0,0,,因为蛇的毒液在进化过程中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.12,0:08:08.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,for potency against their usual prey,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.12,0:08:08.57,CHN,,0,0,0,,会特异性地增强对它们通常猎物的效力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:11.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,in turn, their prey evolved resistance to their venom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:11.89,CHN,,0,0,0,,相应地 它们的猎物也会进化出抵抗力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.89,0:08:13.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,The honey badger, for example,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.89,0:08:13.78,CHN,,0,0,0,,例如蜜獾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.78,0:08:16.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,is almost completely immune to Cobra venom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.78,0:08:16.85,CHN,,0,0,0,,几乎对眼镜蛇毒液完全免疫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:20.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,So the lethality of a bite depends on the snake,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:20.26,CHN,,0,0,0,,因此蛇咬伤的致命性既取决于蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.26,0:08:22.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,the animal that got bitten,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.26,0:08:22.13,CHN,,0,0,0,,也取决于被咬的动物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.13,0:08:24.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,and the amount of venom injected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.13,0:08:24.59,CHN,,0,0,0,,还取决于注入了多少毒液
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.59,0:08:27.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,The reason scientists test different venoms on lab mice
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.59,0:08:27.82,CHN,,0,0,0,,科学家之所以要在小鼠上测试各种毒液
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:30.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,is to get an estimate of the amount of antivenom
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.63,0:08:33.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,that would be required to neutralize a bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:33.35,CHN,,0,0,0,,是为了估计中和咬伤所需的血清用量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.35,0:08:35.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,Snake venom is lethal to us
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.35,0:08:35.37,CHN,,0,0,0,,蛇毒对我们来说是致命的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.37,0:08:38.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,because we are closely related to snakes' main prey,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.37,0:08:38.55,CHN,,0,0,0,,因为人类的亲缘接近蛇类的主要猎物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:39.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,rodents.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:39.58,CHN,,0,0,0,,啮齿动物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.59,0:08:42.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,Rodents and primates split on the evolutionary tree
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.59,0:08:42.59,CHN,,0,0,0,,啮齿动物和灵长动物进化上的分叉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.59,0:08:45.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,only 75 million years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.59,0:08:45.00,CHN,,0,0,0,,距今仅 7500 万年
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:47.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,so we share a lot of the same biology,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:47.43,CHN,,0,0,0,,因此我们有很多共同的生物学特征
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.43,0:08:50.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,from the structure of our cells to the way our blood clots,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.43,0:08:50.71,CHN,,0,0,0,,从我们的细胞结构 到凝血方式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.71,0:08:53.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,to how our nerves send signals.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.71,0:08:53.24,CHN,,0,0,0,,再到神经信号的传递
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:58.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Venoms typically target very conserved molecular pathways
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:58.10,CHN,,0,0,0,,毒液通常针对广泛保有的分子通路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:09:00.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,that exist across maybe all vertebrates
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:09:00.74,CHN,,0,0,0,,这些通路几乎存在于所有脊椎动物中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.74,0:09:05.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,or maybe even the entire tree of life in some cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.74,0:09:05.11,CHN,,0,0,0,,有的甚至存在于几乎所有物种
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:10.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,There are four ways that snake venom can kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:10.13,CHN,,0,0,0,,蛇毒通常有四种方式杀死你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:11.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,It can be neurotoxic,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:11.84,CHN,,0,0,0,,它可能有神经毒性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.84,0:09:14.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,damaging to your nervous system and brain
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.84,0:09:14.18,CHN,,0,0,0,,通过干扰神经递质
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.18,0:09:16.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,by interfering with neurotransmitters,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.18,0:09:16.38,CHN,,0,0,0,,即神经元之间传递信号的化学物质
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.38,0:09:19.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,the signaling chemicals that go between neurons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.38,0:09:19.25,CHN,,0,0,0,,损伤你的大脑和神经系统
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.25,0:09:21.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,It can be hemotoxic,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.25,0:09:21.09,CHN,,0,0,0,,它可能有血液毒性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.09,0:09:21.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,thinning out your blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.09,0:09:21.93,CHN,,0,0,0,,稀释你的血液
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.93,0:09:23.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,preventing wounds from healing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.93,0:09:23.77,CHN,,0,0,0,,阻止伤口愈合
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:25.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,and causing internal bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:25.83,CHN,,0,0,0,,并造成内出血
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:28.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,It does this by disturbing the delicate machinery
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.28,0:09:30.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,of the blood coagulation system.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:30.48,CHN,,0,0,0,,通过扰乱凝血的精密过程可以做到这些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:32.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,Venom can also be cytotoxic,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:32.71,CHN,,0,0,0,,毒液也可能有细胞毒性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:35.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,attacking cells, leading to severe blisters,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:35.30,CHN,,0,0,0,,攻击细胞 产生严重的水泡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:37.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,necrosis and cell death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:37.73,CHN,,0,0,0,,坏疽和细胞死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.73,0:09:39.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,It can also be myotoxic,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.73,0:09:39.76,CHN,,0,0,0,,它还可以有肌肉毒性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:43.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,destroying muscles and causing paralysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:43.08,CHN,,0,0,0,,摧毁肌肉并导致瘫痪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:45.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,The worst part is that snake venoms
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:45.05,CHN,,0,0,0,,更糟糕的事情是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.05,0:09:47.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,can contain up to 200 compounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.05,0:09:47.68,CHN,,0,0,0,,蛇毒可包含高达 200 种化合物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.68,0:09:50.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,Most venoms contain a combination of neurotoxic,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.68,0:09:50.45,CHN,,0,0,0,,大多数毒液中含有多种毒性蛋白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:54.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,hemotoxic, cytotoxic and myotoxic proteins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:54.64,CHN,,0,0,0,,能同时具有神经毒性、血液毒性、细胞毒性和肌肉毒性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.64,0:09:57.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is what makes snake bites so difficult to treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.64,0:09:57.89,CHN,,0,0,0,,因此蛇咬伤才如此难以治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:10:00.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's not just one toxin you're trying to neutralize,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:10:00.96,CHN,,0,0,0,,你不仅仅是需要中和一种毒素
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.96,0:10:04.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,but dozens all working together to try to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.96,0:10:04.22,CHN,,0,0,0,,而是数十种试图一同杀死你的毒素
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.81,0:10:07.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.81,0:10:07.19,CHN,,0,0,0,,过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:08.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:08.02,CHN,,0,0,0,,乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.02,0:10:09.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.02,0:10:09.02,CHN,,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.47,0:10:14.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,I've been at the park for 10 years this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.47,0:10:14.22,CHN,,0,0,0,,这已经是我在这个公园的第 10 个年头了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:18.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,I've been running this facility for 7 1/2, eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:18.16,CHN,,0,0,0,,我在这处设施得有七年半……八年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.16,0:10:19.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,Have you ever been bitten?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.16,0:10:19.56,CHN,,0,0,0,,你被咬过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.94,0:10:25.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so about 3 1/2 years ago, I got a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.94,0:10:25.52,CHN,,0,0,0,,啊 有的 大约三年半之前 我被划伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:29.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,One finger got nicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:29.00,CHN,,0,0,0,,一根手指被划伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:31.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,That was 36 hours in ICU
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:31.04,CHN,,0,0,0,,在重症监护待了 36 个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:33.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,and eight of those were on a resus bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:33.28,CHN,,0,0,0,,其中 8 小时是在抢救室
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:34.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,So very, very serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:34.78,CHN,,0,0,0,,非常非常严重
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:36.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,And what was that experience like?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:36.32,CHN,,0,0,0,,那是一种怎样的体验？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:37.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,That was crappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:37.20,CHN,,0,0,0,,那真是糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:38.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,As it turns out,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:38.03,CHN,,0,0,0,,事实证明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.03,0:10:40.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm highly allergic to antivenom, which is not ideal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.03,0:10:40.06,CHN,,0,0,0,,我对抗蛇毒血清高度过敏 这可不是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.06,0:10:42.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,I started swelling up looking like the Elephant Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.06,0:10:42.38,CHN,,0,0,0,,我浑身肿胀 看起来好似“象人”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.38,0:10:44.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,So then they whack you with adrenaline
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:45.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,to cancel out the anaphylaxis
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.38,0:10:45.42,CHN,,0,0,0,,他们接着给你打肾上腺素抵抗过敏反应
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.42,0:10:47.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,and then they have to give you more anti-venom,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.42,0:10:47.21,CHN,,0,0,0,,然后他们必须给你打更多血清
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:48.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,more adrenaline, more anti-venom, more adrenaline,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:48.97,CHN,,0,0,0,,更多肾上腺素 更多血清 更多肾上腺素
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.97,0:10:50.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,more anti-venom, more adrenaline.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.97,0:10:50.30,CHN,,0,0,0,,更多血清 更多肾上腺素……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:52.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,And thankfully, I only needed the one,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:52.09,CHN,,0,0,0,,谢天谢地 我只需要第一剂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.09,0:10:53.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,but it was like the best case scenario,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.09,0:10:53.37,CHN,,0,0,0,,这应该是不幸中的万幸了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.37,0:10:54.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,he didn't chew, he didn't bite,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.37,0:10:54.61,CHN,,0,0,0,,蛇没有实际上咬到我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:56.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,but literally just a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:56.54,CHN,,0,0,0,,仅仅是划伤而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.54,0:10:58.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,So what is antivenom exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.54,0:10:58.61,CHN,,0,0,0,,那么抗蛇毒血清到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.61,0:11:00.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,and how was it invented?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.61,0:11:00.48,CHN,,0,0,0,,它又是如何被发明的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:04.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,In 1870, a British military doctor, Edward Nicholson
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:04.84,CHN,,0,0,0,,1870年 一位英国军医爱德华·尼克森
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.84,0:11:06.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,was stationed in Burma,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.84,0:11:06.78,CHN,,0,0,0,,在缅甸驻扎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.78,0:11:09.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,and as he watched the local snake handlers,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.78,0:11:09.36,CHN,,0,0,0,,他在观察当地的驯蛇师时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.36,0:11:11.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,he noticed something strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.36,0:11:11.52,CHN,,0,0,0,,注意到了一件奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.52,0:11:13.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,They would from time to time
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.66,0:11:16.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,deliberately get Cobras to bite them
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.52,0:11:16.36,CHN,,0,0,0,,驯蛇师偶尔会故意让眼镜蛇咬他们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:19.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,in what he considered a form of tattooing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:19.20,CHN,,0,0,0,,他起初认为这是某种纹身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:20.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,Nicholson reasoned that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:20.36,CHN,,0,0,0,,他后来推断
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.36,0:11:23.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,they were intentionally exposing their bodies to the venom
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.36,0:11:23.40,CHN,,0,0,0,,驯蛇师是有意让自己的身体接触蛇毒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.40,0:11:25.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,to develop an immune response.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.40,0:11:25.99,CHN,,0,0,0,,来逐渐加强对蛇毒的免疫反应
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:28.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,He observed that the older snake handlers
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:28.52,CHN,,0,0,0,,他注意到年长的驯蛇师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:30.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,were less affected by accidental bites
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:30.42,CHN,,0,0,0,,受到意外咬伤的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.42,0:11:31.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,than the younger ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.42,0:11:31.67,CHN,,0,0,0,,比年轻驯蛇师更小
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:35.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,So this dangerous practice seemed to be paying off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:35.53,CHN,,0,0,0,,所以这种危险的做法似乎很有效
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.32,0:11:39.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,20 years later in Saigon,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.32,0:11:39.06,CHN,,0,0,0,,20 年后的越南西贡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.06,0:11:40.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,a French medical researcher named
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.06,0:11:40.86,CHN,,0,0,0,,一位法国医学研究员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.86,0:11:42.07,CHN,,0,0,0,,阿尔贝·卡尔梅特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:45.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,was vaccinating local residents against smallpox.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:45.25,CHN,,0,0,0,,在为当地居民接种天花疫苗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.25,0:11:48.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,When he became aware of the threat posed by Cobras,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.25,0:11:48.47,CHN,,0,0,0,,他在了解到眼镜蛇对人类的威胁之后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:49.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,he wondered if it was possible
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:49.93,CHN,,0,0,0,,就想知道是否有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:52.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,to make a vaccine for snake bites.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:52.67,CHN,,0,0,0,,制出对抗蛇咬的疫苗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.67,0:11:55.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,Back in Paris, he tried injecting rabbits
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.67,0:11:55.16,CHN,,0,0,0,,回到巴黎后  他尝试给兔子注射
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.16,0:11:57.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,with a tiny amount of Cobra venom
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.16,0:11:57.66,CHN,,0,0,0,,微量的眼镜蛇毒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.66,0:12:01.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,starting with just .03 milligrams,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.66,0:12:01.13,CHN,,0,0,0,,从 0.03 毫克开始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.13,0:12:03.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,but each week, he injected the rabbits again
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.13,0:12:03.85,CHN,,0,0,0,,之后的每周他会继续给兔子注射
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.85,0:12:06.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,slowly increasing the dose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.85,0:12:06.31,CHN,,0,0,0,,并逐渐增加剂量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.31,0:12:07.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,And after eight months of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.31,0:12:07.86,CHN,,0,0,0,,在持续了 8 个月之后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.86,0:12:09.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,the rabbits were receiving
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.86,0:12:09.05,CHN,,0,0,0,,兔子们每次注射
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.05,0:12:12.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,35 milligrams of Cobra venom at a time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.05,0:12:12.09,CHN,,0,0,0,,就要接受 35 毫克的眼镜蛇毒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.09,0:12:16.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,that is 15 times the normal lethal dose in rabbits,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.09,0:12:16.28,CHN,,0,0,0,,这是兔子正常情况下致死量的 15 倍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.28,0:12:19.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,but they were still perfectly healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.28,0:12:19.01,CHN,,0,0,0,,但它们却仍然非常健康
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.01,0:12:21.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,The rabbits' immune systems had developed antibodies
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.01,0:12:21.76,CHN,,0,0,0,,兔子们的免疫系统产生了抗体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:23.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,to neutralize the venom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:23.68,CHN,,0,0,0,,来中和蛇毒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:26.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,So you can be vaccinated against snake bites
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:26.30,CHN,,0,0,0,,所以我们可以像对抗疾病那样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:28.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,just as you can against disease,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:28.57,CHN,,0,0,0,,接种抗蛇毒的疫苗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:29.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,but who wants to be vaccinated
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:29.96,CHN,,0,0,0,,但谁又想接种所有种类的疫苗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.96,0:12:32.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,against all different types of snakes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.96,0:12:32.28,CHN,,0,0,0,,来对抗所有的蛇毒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.28,0:12:34.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,just in case one bites you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.28,0:12:34.07,CHN,,0,0,0,,而仅仅就因为被一条蛇咬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.07,0:12:35.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,It would be better, Calmette reasoned,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.07,0:12:35.81,CHN,,0,0,0,,他推断 要是能在被咬之后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:39.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,if you could administer antibodies after a bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:39.65,CHN,,0,0,0,,能把抗体注射进去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:42.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,So he drew blood from a venom resistant rabbit
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:42.51,CHN,,0,0,0,,所以他抽出了抗蛇毒兔子的血
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.51,0:12:45.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,and isolated the serum which contains the antibodies,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.51,0:12:45.92,CHN,,0,0,0,,将含有抗体的血清分离出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.92,0:12:48.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,and then he injected it into another rabbit
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.92,0:12:48.43,CHN,,0,0,0,,然后把血清注射给一只
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.43,0:12:51.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,that had never been exposed to venom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.43,0:12:51.11,CHN,,0,0,0,,从未接触过蛇毒的兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.11,0:12:53.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,When he subsequently injected it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.11,0:12:53.01,CHN,,0,0,0,,当他随后给这只兔子注射了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.01,0:12:55.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,with twice the lethal dose of Cobra venom,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.01,0:12:55.53,CHN,,0,0,0,,两倍致死量的眼睛蛇毒之后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.53,0:12:57.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,the rabbit was just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.53,0:12:57.86,CHN,,0,0,0,,这只兔子毫发无伤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.86,0:13:01.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Immunity had been transferred from one rabbit to another.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.86,0:13:01.68,CHN,,0,0,0,,对蛇毒的免疫力从一只兔子转移到了另一只兔子上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.68,0:13:04.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,This was the first antivenom,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.68,0:13:04.05,CHN,,0,0,0,,这就是世界上第一个抗蛇毒血清
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.05,0:13:07.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,or as the Frenchman, Calmette called it, antivenin,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.05,0:13:07.71,CHN,,0,0,0,,或者 这位法国人叫它 Antivenin
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.71,0:13:11.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,which is why my phone always makes that auto-correction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.71,0:13:11.26,CHN,,0,0,0,,这是我手机键盘一直自动更正的原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:14.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,To this day, antivenoms are made in much the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:14.96,CHN,,0,0,0,,抗蛇毒血清的制作方法  一直以来变化不大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:16.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,At the Reptile Park,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:16.15,CHN,,0,0,0,,在爬行动物公园里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.15,0:13:18.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,they collect and freeze the venom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.15,0:13:18.23,CHN,,0,0,0,,工作人员收集蛇毒并冷冻起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:19.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's sent off to be diluted
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:19.71,CHN,,0,0,0,,蛇毒被送去稀释
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.71,0:13:24.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,and injected into a donor animal, usually a horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.71,0:13:24.00,CHN,,0,0,0,,然后被注射到一只供体动物体内 通常是马
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:26.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,Horses are used because of their size.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:26.61,CHN,,0,0,0,,用马作供体动物  是因为马体型庞大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:29.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,After increasing the dose over a period of months,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:29.39,CHN,,0,0,0,,在数月内  逐渐增加注射的剂量之后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:31.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,the horse builds up immunity to the venom,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:31.86,CHN,,0,0,0,,马就会对这种蛇毒免疫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.86,0:13:33.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,and then it's blood is drawn
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.86,0:13:33.58,CHN,,0,0,0,,然后人们把马的血抽出
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:35.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,and the antibodies are isolated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:35.62,CHN,,0,0,0,,从中分离出抗体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:36.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,Only the plasma is taken,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:36.99,CHN,,0,0,0,,提取时只取血浆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.99,0:13:39.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,the red blood cells are returned to the horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.99,0:13:39.86,CHN,,0,0,0,,红细胞会被注射回马体内
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:44.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,Those horse antibodies are the life saving antivenom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:44.67,CHN,,0,0,0,,这些马的抗体  就是能救命的抗蛇毒血清
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:47.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Antivenom works for the same reason venom works,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:47.70,CHN,,0,0,0,,抗蛇毒血清在人体内的工作机理  和蛇毒相似
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.70,0:13:49.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,because of our shared evolutionary history
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.83,0:13:51.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,with other mammals.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.70,0:13:51.35,CHN,,0,0,0,,因为我们和其他哺乳动物  有着共同的进化历史
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:53.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,The antibodies produced by horses
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:53.30,CHN,,0,0,0,,马产生的抗体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.30,0:13:56.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,are very similar to the ones produced by humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.30,0:13:56.08,CHN,,0,0,0,,和人类产生的抗体非常相似
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.08,0:13:58.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,so they bind to toxic compounds and neutralize them
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.08,0:13:58.91,CHN,,0,0,0,,因此也能和毒素结合 并中和它们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.91,0:14:00.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,even in our bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.91,0:14:00.96,CHN,,0,0,0,,哪怕是在人类体内
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.96,0:14:04.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,But this way of making antivenom has downsides.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.96,0:14:04.20,CHN,,0,0,0,,但是这种制备抗蛇毒血清的方式也有缺点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.20,0:14:06.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,Collecting the venom is dangerous,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.20,0:14:06.31,CHN,,0,0,0,,收集蛇毒的过程非常危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.31,0:14:08.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,many donor animals are involved,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.31,0:14:08.43,CHN,,0,0,0,,需要很多很多供体动物参与
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.43,0:14:12.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,and some people are allergic to antivenom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.43,0:14:12.07,CHN,,0,0,0,,而且有些人对抗蛇毒血清过敏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.07,0:14:14.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,Scientists are now exploring the possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.07,0:14:14.19,CHN,,0,0,0,,科学家正在探索另一种可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.19,0:14:17.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,of producing antivenom using genetically modified bacteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.19,0:14:17.96,CHN,,0,0,0,,用修改过基因的细菌来生产抗蛇毒血清
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:20.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,They would produce the specific antibodies
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:20.41,CHN,,0,0,0,,这些细菌可以产生
